Resource Profile: Practitioner Role

Official URL: http://va.gov/fhir/StructureDefinition/PractitionerRole Version: 1.4.15
Active as of 2025-04-30 Computable Name: PractitionerRole

This StructureDefinition contains the maps for VistA file NEW PERSON (200) to us-core-practitionerrole.

​See also the FHIR Shorthand.

Use Case Overview

Usage:

  • CapabilityStatements using this Resource Profile: Debt Portal and Lighthouse Patient Health API
  • This Resource Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide
